, the burst duration decreases and ends in each group the PRE bursts\noccurred. This provides new clues to the type-I bursts in the context of\noutbursts for atoll XRBs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Feb 2010 17:41:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
